<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id78057075-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id78057076-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2026—Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/119/91">Pub. L. 119–91</ref> substituted “57,728” for “48,438”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
